name: HOLE (MaximeGammaitoni, Strik, thebananeman, Jipey)
description:
You've been locked out of hell and you're trying to go back. However it will not be an easy task. You will have to survive avoiding all the obstacles and traps that are set along the way to prevent anyone from getting to hell. Your only weapon in this tough journey is your dash. Good luck going back down to hell.

Little bug fix : - Leader board ordered
